     H            Y.
     F** ANZR@1 *********************************************
     F*安全在庫理由ファイルのコンバージョン               *
     F*       HOTTA.           2018.08.29                   *
     F********************************************* ANZR09 **
     FAAFPP01 UF  E                    DISK
     FAAHPP01 UF  E                    DISK
     I           SDS
     I                                        1  10 PGMNM
     I                                       91 170 MSGTXT
     I                                      244 253 WSID
     I                                      254 263 USID
     I                                      264 269 JBNO
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80A3STYD
     I                                        1   40A3STYY
     I                                        5   60A3STMM
     I                                        7   80A3STDD
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80L6STYD
     I                                        1   40L6STYY
     I                                        5   60L6STMM
     I                                        7   80L6STDD
      *めっき
     C                     READ AAFPP011                 80
     C           *IN80     DOWEQ'0'
     C           A3SKJY    IFEQ *BLANK
     C           A3STYD    ANDGE*DATE
     C                     ADD  A3PADJ    A3AUAJ
     C                     Z-ADD0         A3PADJ
     C                     UPDATAAFPP011
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     READ AAFPP011                 80
     C                     ENDDO
      *引取
     C                     READ AAHPP011                 80
     C           *IN80     DOWEQ'0'
     C           L6SKJY    IFEQ *BLANK
     C           L6STYD    ANDGE*DATE
     C                     ADD  L6PADJ    L6AUAJ
     C                     Z-ADD0         L6PADJ
     C                     UPDATAAHPP011
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     READ AAHPP011                 80
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
